─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Desert Stress Monitor – Server Environment
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Server
PORT=3001
NODE_ENV=development

─── Aiven Cloud PostgreSQL (primary) ────────────────────────
Leave blank to skip and try local DB instead
DB_HOST=your_aiven_host.aivencloud.com
DB_PORT=18473
DB_NAME=your_database
DB_USER=your_db_user
DB_PASSWORD=your_aiven_password
DB_SSL=true

─── Local PostgreSQL (fallback if Aiven unreachable) ────────
Uncomment and fill in when you have a local PG server running
LOCAL_DB_HOST=localhost
LOCAL_DB_PORT=5432
LOCAL_DB_NAME=desert_stress_monitor
LOCAL_DB_USER=postgres
LOCAL_DB_PASSWORD=your_local_password
LOCAL_DB_SSL=false

─── Auth (required) ─────────────────────────────────────────
Set a strong random string for each (≥32 characters)
SESSION_SECRET=change_to_random_string_in_production
JWT_SECRET=change_to_random_string_in_production
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=24h

─── Gateway Telemetry Ingestion ─────────────────────────────
Set a strong random key for the LoRa gateway to POST telemetry
without a user JWT. If unset, the telemetry endpoint requires
a valid operator JWT instead.
GATEWAY_API_KEY=change_to_random_string_in_production

─── CORS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173

─── Gateway ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
GATEWAY_SERIAL_PORT=
GATEWAY_BAUD_RATE=115200

─── Seed defaults ───────────────────────────────────────────
In production (NODE_ENV=production) both must be set and
ADMIN_PASSWORD must be at least 8 characters. In development,
leaving these blank enables a default admin account.
ADMIN_EMAIL=
ADMIN_PASSWORD=

─── App ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
MAX_ALERTS=1000
DATA_DIR=./data
